rows.label: qst620102_msg0002
rows.name:
Bipopo not expect Tiger! Tiger! be
like this! Look so exciting!

rows.label: qst620102_msg0003
rows.name: Bipopo is Nopon of good tastes!

rows.label: qst620102_msg0007
rows.name:
Of course OK!
But have to pay Tora 100G
for one play.

rows.label: qst620102_msg0008
rows.name:
Is no problemomo.
Bipopo have plenty money.

rows.label: qst620102_msg0012
rows.name:
Nopon can't expect to be 
good at something first time!

rows.label: qst620102_msg0013
rows.name:
Try many time, get good. Then
maybe win glorious prize!

rows.label: qst620102_msg0014
rows.name:
Mehmeh! Tora say prize?! 
For prize, Bipopo try again.
Try much more harder!

rows.label: qst620102_msg0015
rows.name:
Play as much as want!
Tora and friends have relaxing
time inside.

rows.label: qst620102_msg0016
rows.name:
Bipopo! Is been two hours.
How is gamerpon doing?

rows.label: qst620102_msg0020
rows.name:
But Tiger! Tiger! is pinnacle of
Nopon game artistry!
Why Bipopo think is terrible?

rows.label: qst620102_msg0023
rows.name:
If no terrible game, then what?
Stealing from poor Bipopo...

rows.label: qst620102_msg0025
rows.name:
That mean one dying every
15 seconds! Is preposterous!
Bipopo terrible, not game!

rows.label: qst620102_msg0029
rows.name:
Well, Bipopo think about it. 
And game so fun, Bipopo keep
playing. Spend all money.

rows.label: qst620102_msg0033
rows.name:
Bipopo regret not getting prize.
Wanted to at least get souvenir...and
Tank Mod III is good souvenir...

rows.label: qst620102_msg0034
rows.name:
Tora can helping there! As
gesture, Tora get prize for
Bipopo.

rows.label: qst620102_msg0035
rows.name:
Mehmeh! Really?
Oh thank you, thank you!

rows.label: qst620102_msg0036
rows.name:
Bipopo look forward to see top-tier 
gaming talent of Tora put to good use!
